{"tid":47954,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"看著時間慢慢流逝, 但什麼都沒有進步","createTime":"2016-12-20T17:06:57.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-22T00:52:23.000Z","uid":24660,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"379de6c345aa4c94a3a7dbbce37a5bca79b487d7","tid":47954,"uid":24660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T17:06:57.000Z","msg":"看著時間慢慢流逝, 但什麼都沒有進步 <br />\n這種感覺很可怕 <br />\n其實回想過去, 在事業上, 叫努力過, 盡過力 <br />\n但香港濕9公司, 濕9老細何其多, 對於他們來說, 他們覺得你努力是應份, 不努力連工都無得番 <br />\n看著自己慢慢地年老, 看著時間一點一點地溜去 <br />\n這麼快就完了2016年, 歲月不饒人 <br />\n體力明顯也差以前很多 <br />\n但自己又可以點呀 <br />\n好像一切都無能為力, 想改變又無從入手 <br />\n看見香港慢慢地進入死亡深淵, 作為一個基層, 當然也被這個時代的洪流捲入去, 但又可以怎樣呢 <br />\n唉, 身不由己, 這麼快那麼快就中年, 很多變成老人家了"},{"pid":"f0ea8f0e2d89c2ba8623d61b393b9ba37e020c5b","tid":47954,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T22:13:31.000Z","msg":"#<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />#fatc"},{"pid":"608658d616f3402a4380b1cda06ecb298450af3b","tid":47954,"uid":28307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T00:53:18.000Z","msg":"樂觀蛇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb81488f1138e06838ed49c51ed687b857230629","tid":47954,"uid":7343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T00:53:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"261c3dee3283ec1d4ec84af6a20c73529fbf9979","tid":47954,"uid":49039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T00:52:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n完全明白"}]}